## Summary

‚Ä¢ Remove temporary files, debug logs, and obsolete prototype kits  
‚Ä¢ Refactor market scraping code for consistency and readability  
‚Ä¢ Clean up technical debt while preserving all functionality  

### Key Changes

**Cleanup:**
- Removed 4,200+ lines of temporary/debug code and prototypes
- Deleted obsolete documentation and fix attempts
- Removed duplicate implementations

**Code Quality:**
- Improved formatting and added meaningful comments
- Consistent error handling patterns
- Better separation of concerns in market providers

**Functionality Preserved:**
- Market data fetching (Yahoo/Google/MarketWatch)
- Yahoo domain control (.com/.co.jp) for currency selection
- Market probe diagnostic API for troubleshooting
- Symbol resolution and price aggregation
- Caching and error handling mechanisms

## Test plan

- [x] Market probe API returns correct data
- [x] Yahoo .com domain fetches USD prices
- [x] Symbol resolution works for major tickers
- [x] Price aggregation handles single/multiple sources
- [x] Error handling for failed providers
